metadata.name: [Meatnugget] - Order
metadata.description:
That meaty spark of consciousness seems to come from nowhere and with it follows aeons of collected wisdom, fear, pain, joy and cold hard data. We have 9 months to put it together before we're launched out of a miraculous meat cannon to put it all to the test... 

Godspeed Meatnugget.

This particular piece "Order" centers upon the positive information transfer, bolstering our forming egos in utero. 

I've created an uplifting soundscape to vibe with this piece so feel free to crank the volume.

Visuals and Music - CKx
